* time

  - elapsed time (ELA)
  - if total size is known, estimated total time (ETT=ELA/progress)
  - if total size is known, estimated time remaining (ETR=ETT-ELA)
  - if total size is known, estimated timestamp of completion

* input side

  - bytes read
  - if total size is known, total size (either read or given at command line)
  - if total size is known, bytes remaining
